        <h2 id="mesh-heading" class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-ink tracking-wide uppercase mb-8">
          Mesh Belt Types for <span class="text-accent">Cooling</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-5">
          <p>
            Cooling conveyor belt selection balances airflow (open area), product support (mesh size), strength (load capacity), and cleanability. The belt is the primary heat transfer surface , its open area directly affects cooling efficiency.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto -mx-4 px-4 mt-8">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[750px]">
            <thead>
